# NO3D TOOLS DESIGN SYSTEM
## Website Style Guide v1.0

---

## üé® DESIGN PHILOSOPHY

**Core Concept**: Retro-Future Technical Minimalism
- Blend of early computer aesthetics with modern 3D rendering
- Functional brutalism meets playful experimentation  
- Information hierarchy through typography rather than decoration
- Technical precision with organic creativity

---

## üåà COLOR PALETTE

### Primary Colors

**Lello** (Primary Accent)
- HEX: `#f0ff00`
- RGB: `rgb(240, 255, 0)`
- Usage: CTAs, highlights, active states, key information
- Accessibility: Use only on dark backgrounds (AA contrast minimum)

**Deep Charcoal** (Primary Text)
- HEX: `#1A1A1A` / `#242424`
- RGB: `rgb(26, 26, 26)`
- Usage: All body text, headings, monospace content
- Accessibility: AAA contrast on light backgrounds

**Stone Gray** (Background)
- HEX: `#E8E8E8` / `#ECECEC`
- RGB: `rgb(232, 232, 232)`
- Usage: Primary background, canvas, neutral space
- Note: Slightly warm gray, not pure neutral

### Secondary Colors

**Shadow Black** (3D Depth)
- HEX: `#0D0D0D`
- RGB: `rgb(13, 13, 13)`
- Usage: Drop shadows, depth effects, 3D object shadows

**Void Black** (True Black)
- HEX: `#000000`
- RGB: `rgb(0, 0, 0)`
- Usage: Extreme contrast moments, icon fills, borders

**Paper White** (Contrast Background)
- HEX: `#FFFFFF`
- RGB: `rgb(255, 255, 255)`
- Usage: Card backgrounds, input fields, contrast sections

### Accent Colors (3D Objects)

**Lello Light**
- HEX: `#f0ff00`
- Usage: Secondary 3D objects, hover states



---

## üìù TYPOGRAPHY

### Font Stack

**Primary Typeface: Silka Mono (Body Text)**
```css
font-family: 'Silka Mono', 'Courier New', 'Courier', 'Monaco', 'Consolas', 'Liberation Mono', monospace;
```

**Header Typeface: Visitor (Headers, Links, Buttons)**
```css
font-family: 'Visitor', 'Arial Black', 'Arial', sans-serif;
```

**Silka Mono Characteristics:**
- Fixed-width characters
- Technical, computer-terminal aesthetic
- High legibility at all sizes
- Retro-computing nostalgia

**Visitor Characteristics:**
- Bold, geometric sans-serif
- High impact for headers and CTAs
- Excellent readability at large sizes
- Modern, technical aesthetic

### Hierarchy & Sizing

**Display Title (Site Header)**
- Font Family: `Visitor`
- Font Size: `48px` / `3rem`
- Font Weight: `700` (Bold)
- Line Height: `1.0`
- Letter Spacing: `0.15em` (Wide tracking)
- Text Transform: `uppercase`
- Usage: Main site title only
- Example: `NO3D TOOLS`

**H1 - Primary Heading**
- Font Family: `Visitor`
- Font Size: `32px` / `2rem`
- Font Weight: `700`
- Line Height: `1.1`
- Letter Spacing: `0.08em`
- Text Transform: `uppercase`
- Margin Bottom: `24px`

**H2 - Section Heading**
- Font Family: `Visitor`
- Font Size: `24px` / `1.5rem`
- Font Weight: `700`
- Line Height: `1.2`
- Letter Spacing: `0.06em`
- Text Transform: `uppercase`
- Margin Bottom: `16px`
- Example: `CHANGELOG v2.3.1`

**H3 - Subsection**
- Font Family: `Visitor`
- Font Size: `18px` / `1.125rem`
- Font Weight: `600`
- Line Height: `1.3`
- Letter Spacing: `0.04em`
- Margin Bottom: `12px`

**Body Text**
- Font Family: `Silka Mono`
- Font Size: `14px` / `0.875rem`
- Font Weight: `400`
- Line Height: `1.6`
- Letter Spacing: `0.01em`
- Color: `#1A1A1A`
- Max Width: `65ch` (optimal readability)

**Small/Caption Text**
- Font Family: `Silka Mono`
- Font Size: `12px` / `0.75rem`
- Font Weight: `400`
- Line Height: `1.5`
- Letter Spacing: `0.02em`
- Usage: Metadata, version numbers, captions

**Code/Technical Text**
- Font Family: `Silka Mono`
- Font Size: `13px` / `0.8125rem`
- Font Weight: `400`
- Line Height: `1.4`
- Background: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)`
- Padding: `2px 6px`
- Border Radius: `2px`

### ASCII Art Typography

**Dojo Slug Tool Logo Style**
- Character Set: Block characters (‚ñà ‚ñÄ ‚ñÑ ‚ñê ‚ñå)
- Grid: Precise alignment required
- Spacing: Monospace grid system
- Style: Blocky, pixelated, brutalist
- Example characters: Square fills, half blocks
- Padding: Generous whitespace around art

---

## üìê LAYOUT & SPACING

### Grid System

**Desktop Layout (>1024px)**
- Container Max Width: `1440px`
- Content Max Width: `1200px`
- Gutter: `24px`
- Columns: 12-column flexible grid
- Column Gap: `24px`

**Tablet Layout (768px - 1024px)**
- Container: Full width with `32px` padding
- Columns: 8-column grid
- Column Gap: `20px`

**Mobile Layout (<768px)**
- Container: Full width with `16px` padding
- Columns: 4-column grid
- Column Gap: `16px`

### Spacing Scale

**Base Unit: 8px**

```
Micro:     4px   (0.25 unit)
Tiny:      8px   (1 unit)
Small:     16px  (2 units)
Medium:    24px  (3 units)
Large:     32px  (4 units)
XLarge:    48px  (6 units)
XXLarge:   64px  (8 units)
Huge:      96px  (12 units)
Massive:   128px (16 units)
```

### Section Spacing

**Between major sections**: `64px` - `96px`
**Between subsections**: `32px` - `48px`
**Between related elements**: `16px` - `24px`
**Between list items**: `8px` - `12px`

### Sidebar Navigation

**Width**: `200px` - `240px`
**Position**: Fixed left side
**Padding**: `24px 16px`
**Item Spacing**: `8px` vertical
**Hierarchy Indent**: `16px` per level
**Background**: Slightly darker than main (`#DCDCDC`)

