## üé≠ VISUAL STYLE

### 3D Rendered Objects

**Characteristics:**
- Lighting: Bright, studio-quality with strong highlights
- Shadows: Well-defined drop shadows, not too soft
- Materials: Matte to semi-gloss finish
- Geometry: Abstract, geometric, sculptural forms
- Color: Predominantly Lello with variations
- Style: Clean, modern, abstract shapes
- Render Quality: High-fidelity, no low-poly unless intentional

**Object Types:**
- Cylinders (various heights)
- Spheres (solid and gradient)
- Abstract sculptural forms
- Geometric assemblies
- Tools and implements (stylized)
- Diamonds/crystals
- Organic-geometric hybrids

**Layout Usage:**
- Hero sections: Large featured object
- Icon grid: Multiple small objects
- Background: Subtle object placement
- Interactive: Object responds to hover/interaction

### Photography Style

**Not applicable** - This design uses rendered 3D objects exclusively, no photography

### Illustration Style

**ASCII Art:**
- Monochrome (black on light background)
- Block characters and line art
- Precise grid alignment
- Brutalist, minimal aesthetic
- Used for logos and decorative elements

**3D Illustrations:**
- See "3D Rendered Objects" section above

### Iconography

**Style:** Custom 3D rendered objects (not flat icons)
**Fallback:** Simple geometric Unicode symbols
- `‚ñ∂` Triangle right (expand)
- `‚ñº` Triangle down (collapse)
- `‚óè` Bullet point (current item)
- `‚úì` Checkmark
- `√ó` Close/remove
- `‚Üó` External link

---

## üé¨ ANIMATION & INTERACTION

### Transition Timing

**Standard Transitions:**
```css
transition: all 0.2s ease;
```

**Micro-interactions:**
```css
transition: transform 0.15s ease, opacity 0.15s ease;
```

**Page Transitions:**
```css
transition: opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
```

### Hover Effects

**Links:**
- Underline appears: `0.2s ease`
- Color shift to Lello
- No background change

**Buttons:**
- Background lightens slightly
- Lift effect: `translateY(-2px)`
- Shadow appears/expands
- Duration: `0.2s ease`

**Navigation Items:**
- Background fade-in: `0.15s ease`
- Text color shift
- No transform effects

**3D Objects (Optional Enhancement):**
- Subtle rotation: `transform: rotateY(5deg)` over `0.4s ease`
- Slight scale: `transform: scale(1.05)` over `0.3s ease`
- Shadow expansion

### Loading States

**Style:** Minimal, technical
- Spinner: Rotating square or circle outline
- Color: Lello or Deep Charcoal
- Size: `24px` - `32px`
- Line width: `2px`
- Animation: Smooth rotation, `1s linear infinite`

**Alternative:** ASCII loading indicator
```
[||||¬∑¬∑¬∑¬∑] 40%
[||||||||] 100%
```

