## üì± RESPONSIVE BEHAVIOR

### Breakpoints

```css
/* Mobile First Approach */
--mobile: 320px;
--tablet: 768px;
--desktop: 1024px;
--large: 1440px;
--xlarge: 1920px;
```

### Layout Adaptations

**Desktop (>1024px):**
- Sidebar navigation visible (fixed left)
- Multi-column icon grids (3-4 columns)
- Full-width 3D object display
- Horizontal tab navigation

**Tablet (768px - 1024px):**
- Sidebar collapses to hamburger menu
- Icon grid: 2-3 columns
- Reduced padding and spacing (√ó0.75)
- Horizontal tabs maintained

**Mobile (<768px):**
- Hamburger navigation menu
- Single column icon grid
- Full-width CTA buttons
- Stacked tabs (dropdown alternative)
- Reduced font sizes (√ó0.85)
- Touch-friendly targets (min `44px` √ó `44px`)

### Navigation Behavior

**Mobile Menu:**
- Icon: Hamburger (three horizontal lines)
- Position: Top left
- Animation: Slide from left
- Overlay: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)`
- Close: X button top right
- Menu background: Stone Gray

---

## ‚ôø ACCESSIBILITY

### Color Contrast

**Ratios (WCAG 2.1):**
- Body text on background: Minimum **4.5:1** (AA)
- Large text on background: Minimum **3:1** (AA)
- Lello on white: **FAIL** - Use only on dark backgrounds
- Lello on Deep Charcoal: **Pass AAA**
- Deep Charcoal on Stone Gray: **Pass AAA**

### Keyboard Navigation

**Focus Indicators:**
- Visible focus outline: `2px solid #f0ff00`
- Offset: `2px`
- Never remove focus styles
- Tab order follows visual hierarchy

**Shortcuts:**
- Tab: Next focusable element
- Shift+Tab: Previous focusable element
- Enter: Activate button/link
- Space: Activate button
- Escape: Close modals/dropdowns

### Screen Reader Support

**Semantic HTML:**
- Use proper heading hierarchy (h1 ‚Üí h2 ‚Üí h3)
- `<nav>` for navigation sections
- `<main>` for primary content
- `<article>` for self-contained content
- `<aside>` for sidebar content

**ARIA Labels:**
```html
<button aria-label="Download Dojo Slug Tool">DOWNLOAD</button>
<nav aria-label="Main navigation">...</nav>
<img src="icon.png" alt="Geometric lime green cylinder with shadow">
```

**Skip Links:**
```html
<a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Skip to main content</a>
```

### Motion & Animation

**Respect User Preferences:**
```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  * {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

