## üíª CODE SNIPPETS

### CSS Variables (Custom Properties)

```css
:root {
  /* Colors */
  --color-lello: #f0ff00;
  --color-deep-charcoal: #1A1A1A;
  --color-stone-gray: #E8E8E8;
  --color-shadow-black: #0D0D0D;
  --color-void-black: #000000;
  --color-paper-white: #FFFFFF;
  --color-lello-light: #f0ff00;
  
  /* Typography */
  --font-mono: 'Silka Mono', 'Courier New', 'Courier', 'Monaco', 'Consolas', monospace;
  --font-visitor: 'Visitor', 'Arial Black', 'Arial', sans-serif;
  --font-size-base: 14px;
  --font-size-h1: 32px;
  --font-size-h2: 24px;
  --font-size-h3: 18px;
  --font-size-display: 48px;
  --line-height-base: 1.6;
  --letter-spacing-wide: 0.15em;
  --letter-spacing-normal: 0.02em;
  
  /* Spacing */
  --space-unit: 8px;
  --space-micro: calc(var(--space-unit) * 0.5);
  --space-tiny: var(--space-unit);
  --space-small: calc(var(--space-unit) * 2);
  --space-medium: calc(var(--space-unit) * 3);
  --space-large: calc(var(--space-unit) * 4);
  --space-xlarge: calc(var(--space-unit) * 6);
  --space-xxlarge: calc(var(--space-unit) * 8);
  
  /* Layout */
  --container-max-width: 1440px;
  --content-max-width: 1200px;
  --sidebar-width: 220px;
  
  /* Transitions */
  --transition-fast: 0.15s ease;
  --transition-normal: 0.2s ease;
  --transition-slow: 0.3s ease;
  
  /* Shadows */
  --shadow-subtle: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  --shadow-medium: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  --shadow-strong: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  --shadow-lello-glow: 0 4px 12px rgba(240, 255, 0, 0.4);
}
```

### Button Component

```css
.btn-primary {
  /* Reset */
  border: none;
  outline: none;
  
  /* Typography */
  font-family: var(--font-visitor);
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-wide);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  
