## üìã CHECKLIST FOR NEW PAGES

Before launching a new page, verify:

**Visual:**
- [ ] Silka Mono used for body text
- [ ] Visitor used for headers, links, and buttons
- [ ] Lello used only for accents/CTAs
- [ ] Stone gray background applied
- [ ] All spacing follows 8px grid system
- [ ] Sharp corners maintained (no rounding)

**Typography:**
- [ ] Heading hierarchy is correct (h1 ‚Üí h2 ‚Üí h3)
- [ ] All headings are uppercase
- [ ] Letter spacing is appropriately wide
- [ ] Line length doesn't exceed 65-75 characters
- [ ] Text has sufficient contrast (4.5:1 minimum)

**Layout:**
- [ ] Sidebar navigation is functional
- [ ] Layout is responsive across breakpoints
- [ ] Touch targets are minimum 44√ó44px on mobile
- [ ] Generous whitespace around key elements
- [ ] Grid alignment is precise

**Interaction:**
- [ ] All buttons have hover and active states
- [ ] Focus indicators are visible
- [ ] Transitions are smooth (0.2s standard)
- [ ] Navigation is keyboard accessible
- [ ] Loading states are defined

**Accessibility:**
- [ ] Color contrast passes WCAG AA
- [ ] Semantic HTML is used
- [ ] ARIA labels where appropriate
- [ ] Keyboard navigation works
- [ ] Screen reader tested
- [ ] prefers-reduced-motion respected

**Performance:**
- [ ] Images optimized (WebP preferred)
- [ ] Lazy loading implemented
- [ ] CSS minified for production
- [ ] No layout shift during load
- [ ] Fast loading time (<2s)

---

## üé® DESIGN VARIATIONS

### Dark Mode (Optional Extension)

**Colors:**
- Background: `#1A1A1A` ("Charcoal")
- Text: `#E8E8E8` (Stone Gray inverted)
- Accent: `#f0ff00` ("Lello")
- Objects: Adjusted contrast for visibility

**Implementation:**
```css
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    --color-background: #1A1A1A;
    --color-text: #E8E8E8;
    --color-surface: #2A2A2A;
  }
}
```

### Alternate Accent Colors (Brand Extensions)

If creating product-specific variations:

**Product A:** Cyan variant
- Primary: `#00D4FF` (Cyan)
- Keep same structure and rules

**Product B:** Magenta variant
- Primary: `#FF00D4` (Magenta)
- Keep same structure and rules

**Rule:** Only change the accent color, maintain all other design principles

